Listen is the sixth studio album by French DJ and producer David Guetta, released on 21 November 2014. It will feature collaborations with artists from the R&B, hip hop, alternative rock and pop worlds such as Sam Martin, Emeli SandÃƒÂ©, Danny O'Donoghue the lead singer of band The Script, Nicki Minaj, John Legend, Nico & Vinz, Ryan Tedder the lead singer of pop rock band OneRepublic, Sia, Magic!, Bebe Rexha, South African male choral group Ladysmith Black Mambazo, Ms. Dynamite, Elliphant, Birdy, Jaymes Young, Sonny Wilson, Vassy, and Skylar Grey. It also features additional production from his frequent collaborator Giorgio Tuinfort, Avicii, Afrojack, Nicky Romero, Showtek and Stadiumx among others, with additional writing credits from Jason Evigan, Alicia Keys and The-Dream among others.
